   Second in rate of children without health insurance.
</P>
<P>
   Second in births to mothers aged 15-17.
</P>
<P>
   Second in estimated number of undocumented immigrants.
</P>
<P>
   Ninth in percent of children living in poverty.
</P>
<P>
   16th in crime rate.
</P>
